### [CRM App](https://app.cerebrumhub.com/learning/course/course-v1:Cerebrum_Hub+CS0008+2024_T12/home)

The client is a digital agency offering innovative marketing and web design solutions. The company organizes its sales and project management with a simple CRM platform. There are 3 main business processes that are supported by the CRM:

- Collection of potential customers from different marketing channels and organising the marketing activities.

- Preparing offers, negotiating terms with potential customers and signing contracts.

- Managing projects with the signed contracts and tracking the progress of projects.


The goal of this project was to build a stable and well-tested API for the following functionalities of the CRM system:

- Leads management (creation and management of the customerâ€™s database);

- Invitation of new users;

- Funnels management (creation and management of CRM funnels);

- Deals management (creation and management of deals in different funnels.

